### Download
You can download this project in either [zip](https://github.com/corerd/CRDScrollSwitch/zipball/master) or [tar](https://github.com/corerd/CRDScrollSwitch/tarball/master) formats.

You can also clone the project with [Git](https://github.com/corerd/CRDScrollSwitch) by running:
```
$ git clone https://github.com/corerd/CRDScrollSwitch.git
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
